<tbody>

<tr>

<td style="font-size: 10px; color: #000000; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-family: Arial;">Discuss task with GM. GM Assigns a Difficulty.<br>

Assigned difficulty is adjusted based on skills, special abilities, cyphers, equipment, artifacts and applying effort to a task.<br>-1 if you are trained in a skill<br>-2 if you are specialized in a skill<br>-1 per level of Effort applied

</td>

